**Root Cause Analysis:**
1. **Parallelism Underutilization (PRIMARY)** – Only 4.5 of 64 cores effectively used (35% capacity)
   - Customer filtering (1.5M rows) is sequential
   - Orders filtering (15M rows) is sequential
   - Only lineitem scan (60M rows) is parallelized
